{"tid":1742264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"見到呢個求助Post 我覺得我地應該整一個手足基金","createTime":"2019-11-20T16:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T13:08:35.000Z","uid":57221,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a99dba0308c56d893f6112dbab27fac4b33c0785","tid":1742264,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:56:22.000Z","msg":"(求助）被捕過兩次，冇家人支持，想離家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742118</a><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n呢個post大約係講手足自己嘅經歷<br />\n<br />\n但其中有一點好重要同好現實嘅<br />\n</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係錢</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n相信經濟上有困難嘅手足唔單止佢一個<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多其他手足有經濟上嘅困難<br />\n<br />\n我希望有手足可以建立一個<strong>基金</strong><br />\n<br />\n而大約運作嘅方式<br />\n<br />\n就係</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足有難 <br />\n<br />\n百萬支援</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔同於612/星火<br />\n<br />\n呢個基金得</span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>兩種</strong></span></span>功能<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收錢<br />\n<br />\n比錢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果係證明左被捕/被告/損壞賠償<strong>（黨鐵24萬）</strong><br />\n需要錢去幫手<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地直接就比錢<br />\n唔洗講咁多廢話</span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>即使你冇任何證明<br />\n但核對完你係手足之後<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">（核對方法可以再討論） </span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地一樣比錢支援！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推到有手足成立呢個基金！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"03404f01ba79b809a353ae44b494a1281c51b0b1","tid":1742264,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推到有人成立手足基金！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"61ac7455036dbb231b0b6a3c2072231638eb7868","tid":1742264,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:57:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Push for me！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1b95eeb7a648d9fd977c667362e47af27af6f073","tid":1742264,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:10:09.000Z","msg":"ppp"},{"pid":"ffe3db69f663b818e4388875e88846a79695f943","tid":1742264,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b825c38c10731310170ee59755c7c9cb6b5f143e","tid":1742264,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffe3db69f663b818e4388875e88846a79695f943","tid":1742264,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"pp"},{"pid":"7f359feb4a0b62a8dd26ef73251d597d4cf6dcf0","tid":1742264,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"ppp"},{"pid":"e1d3a11d1e8e1d8efb7c083b54db22c1e7ba1026","tid":1742264,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:17:08.000Z","msg":"大概要幾多"},{"pid":"d6c50a08159067833ba390fc9d83811d814